<lb n="0726c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0726c07" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi">他</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">補</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1B6;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00612;<note n="0726012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">閉＋（二合）細註【甲】</note><app n="0726012"><lem wit="【大】">閉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">閉<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">補</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1B6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00612;閉</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0BC;</t><t lang="chi">蘇</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">補</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1B6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00612;閉</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0726c08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0726c09" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑縛</zi><sg>二<note n="0726013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【甲】＊</note><app n="0726013"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0726c10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0726c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0726c1101">第二埏埴作泥團時。作<tt place="inline"><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0726014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&SD-CFC5;〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0726014"><lem wit="【大】">&SD-CFC5;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">婀</t></tt>字觀。此是如來
<lb n="0726c12" ed="T"/>法界身。先當歸命作如是言。</p>
<lb n="0726c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0726c1301" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi">謨</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">捺</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A663;</t><t lang="chi">闍</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A8;</t><t lang="chi">溺</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6BC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>崛芻</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B6BE;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>悉底</zi><sg><note n="0726015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0726015"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">耶</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">捺</t></tt>
