<lb n="0727a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a0901">第三次於泥團作<tt place="inline"><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0727003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&SD-CDF1;〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0727003"><lem wit="【大】">&SD-CDF1;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi><note n="0727004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝婆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0727004"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">婆</rdg></app>頗</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>字觀。當觀此
<lb n="0727a10" ed="T"/>泥團猶如水精。又如頗胝迦寶。內外清淨分
<lb n="0727a11" ed="T"/>明瑩徹。以陀羅尼加持一遍。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a1201" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日羅</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC9;</t><t lang="chi">嗢</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">皤</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">耶</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0727a13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727a14" ed="T"/><note resp="CBETA.Eva">為配合悉漢對照，故將p727a14中文與p727a15悉曇字前後對調</note><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a1601">第四次塗赤土時。作火色觀。即知一切世間
<lb n="0727a17" ed="T"/>出世間法。皆從微塵而得成就。作此觀已。取
<lb n="0727a18" ed="T"/>乾赤土遍塗泥團。觀一切法本來無生畢竟
<lb n="0727a19" ed="T"/>空寂。作<tt place="inline"><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0727005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&SD-A6B2;〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0727005"><lem wit="【大】">&SD-A6B2;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">含</t></tt>字觀。想此泥團如鎔金色。然
<lb n="0727a20" ed="T"/>後造塔。以陀羅尼加持一遍。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a2101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A658;</t><t lang="chi">尾</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0727006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引）細註【甲】＊</note><app n="0727006"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727a22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a2301">第五次以泥團入模時。用陀羅尼加持一遍。
<lb n="0727a24" ed="T"/>然後入模。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a2501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">入</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日羅</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57C;</t><t lang="chi">馱</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55B;</t><t lang="chi">都</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00617;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B757;</t><t lang="chi">陛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727a2701">第六次入法身真言時。用此陀羅尼加持一
<lb n="0727a28" ed="T"/>遍。然後入印子中。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<pb n="0727b" id="T19.1026.0727b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b0101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57B;</t><t lang="chi">達</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1BA;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57C;</t><t lang="chi">馱</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55B;</t><t lang="chi">都</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00617;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B757;</t><t lang="chi">陛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi">娑<note n="0727007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00085;＋（二合引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0727007"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b0301">第七次<note n="0727008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">椎＝推&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0727008"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">推</rdg></app>打塔印時。用陀羅尼加持一遍。然
<lb n="0727b04" ed="T"/>後<app source="0727008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">推</rdg></app>打。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b0501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">入</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日囉</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">補</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5AD;</t><t lang="chi">特</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A464;</t><t lang="chi">伽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A444;</t><t lang="chi">拘</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4DA;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">耶</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】">&SD-A444;&SD-A4DA;&SD-A5F1;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&SD-D957;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">拘吒耶</t></tt>
<lb n="0727b06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b07" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b0901">第八次<app source="0727008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">推</rdg></app>打竟。以手作塔階時。用陀羅尼加
<lb n="0727b10" ed="T"/>持一遍。安置塔階。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b1101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">入</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日羅</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">喻</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A674;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0727009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曬＋（二合）細註【甲】</note><app n="0727009"><lem wit="【大】">曬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曬<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b1301">第九次塔正從模中出時。用陀羅尼加持一
<lb n="0727b14" ed="T"/>遍。然後出之。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b1501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57B;</t><t lang="chi">達</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1BA;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A559;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A666;</t><t lang="chi">珠</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b1701">第十次脫<note n="0727010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塔＋（了塔）【甲】</note><app n="0727010"><lem wit="【大】">塔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">塔了塔</rdg></app>出模已安置塔時。用陀羅尼加
<lb n="0727b18" ed="T"/>持一遍。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b1901" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0BC;</t><t lang="chi">蘇</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AABC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00425;羅</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A559;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CD4D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>瑟恥</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">入</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi><yin><zi>日</zi><sg><note n="0727011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔入〕－【甲】</note><app n="0727011"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin>羅</zi><sg>二<app source="0726013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0727b20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b21" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二<app source="0726013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b2301">第十一次安置塔座了。以手按塔頂上。以陀
<lb n="0727b24" ed="T"/>羅尼加持一遍。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0727b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b2501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5BF;&SD-A64A;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>跛羅藍</zi><sg>三合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">哆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E040;</t><t lang="chi">喃</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>平</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727b2701">第十二次於塔上安傘蓋時。以陀羅尼加持
<lb n="0727b28" ed="T"/>一遍。陀羅尼曰。</p>
<pb n="0727c" id="T19.1026.0727c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727c0101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5BF;&SD-A64A;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>跛羅藍</zi><sg>三合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">婀</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><app><lem resp="CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】">&SD-A5F9;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&SD-E242;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">喻</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曬</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二<app source="0726013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0727006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0727c02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0727c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727c0301">佛告大王。若善男子善女人。以清淨心依此
<lb n="0727c04" ed="T"/>軌儀造作佛塔。若自作若教人作。若復讚歎
<lb n="0727c05" ed="T"/>若當信受。所得功德與造佛塔等無差別。當
<lb n="0727c06" ed="T"/>知是人於此一生。不為一切毒藥所中。壽命
<lb n="0727c07" ed="T"/>長遠無有橫死。究竟當得不壞之身。一切鬼
<lb n="0727c08" ed="T"/>神不敢逼近。五星七曜隨順驅使。一切怨家
<lb n="0727c09" ed="T"/>悉皆退散。隨所生處身常無病。一切眾生見
<lb n="0727c10" ed="T"/>皆歡喜。無淨戒者淨戒滿足。不調伏者能令
<lb n="0727c11" ed="T"/>調伏。不清淨者能令清淨。破齋戒者齋戒復
<lb n="0727c12" ed="T"/>生。若犯四重及五無間極重罪業悉得消滅。
<lb n="0727c13" ed="T"/>無始劫來障累皆盡。若有女人欲求男者。即
<lb n="0727c14" ed="T"/>生勇健福德之男。四大天王常隨擁護。造塔
<lb n="0727c15" ed="T"/>功德其福如是。若塔破壞變作<note n="0727012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔微〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0727012"><lem wit="【大】">微</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>塵。風吹一
<lb n="0727c16" ed="T"/>塵散落他處。塵所經過山林河海。一切眾生
<lb n="0727c17" ed="T"/>觸斯塵者。永更不受雜類之身。捨身受生常
<lb n="0727c18" ed="T"/>得見佛。大王若善男子善女人。若於造塔及
<lb n="0727c19" ed="T"/>陀羅尼。想觀分明一心憶念。<note n="0727013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔永離〕－【甲】</note><app n="0727013"><lem wit="【大】">永離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>水難火難
<lb n="0727c20" ed="T"/>王難賊難。刀兵等難無能傷害。若於曠野若
<lb n="0727c21" ed="T"/><note n="0727014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">空＋（處）&M062403;【原】，空＝高【甲】</note><app n="0727014"><lem wit="【大】">空</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">空處</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">高</rdg></app>閑處。若於聚落及大會中。能以此經宣
<lb n="0727c22" ed="T"/><note n="0727015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＝旨&M062403;【原】，示【甲】</note><note n="0727015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＝旨&M062403;【原】，＝示【甲】</note><app n="0727015"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">旨</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">示</rdg></app>大眾。即為救護眾生身命。所獲福德量與
<lb n="0727c23" ed="T"/>空等。若於後世書寫流通。塔雖未造<note n="0727016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">造塔功德＝而興造塔【甲】</note><app n="0727016"><lem wit="【大】">造塔功
<lb n="0727c24" ed="T"/>德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">而興造塔</rdg></app>等無有異。我為大王及未來世一切眾生。
<lb n="0727c25" ed="T"/>廣開造塔延命功德。王當憶持。</p>
<lb n="0727c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0727c2601">爾時波斯匿王及諸大眾。聞佛所說皆大歡
<lb n="0727c27" ed="T"/>喜信受奉行。</p></div1>
<lb n="0727c28" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說造塔延命功德經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0727c29" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT19p0727c2901">　<note n="0727017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下檗本無之</note>中天竺三藏牟尼室利　　　<note n="0727018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝證【甲】</note><app n="0727018"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">證</rdg></app>梵語</p>
<pb n="0728a" id="T19.1026.0728a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0728a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0728a0101">　　西明寺大德賜紫沙門圓照　筆　授</p>
<lb n="0728a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0728a0201">　　章<note n="0728001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝敬【甲】</note><app n="0728001"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">敬</rdg></app>寺大德沙門鑑虛　　　潤<note n="0728002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此次行甲本有貞元二十年十一月三日譯畢八日進上十六字</note>文</p>
<lb n="0728a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0728a0301"><note n="0728003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本無之</note><note n="0728003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔靈雲校本云貞享四丁卯稔中春二十三日一校了淨嚴(四十九載)〕－【甲】</note><app n="0728003"><lem wit="【大】">靈雲校本云　貞享四丁卯稔中春二十三
<lb n="0728a04" ed="T"/>日一校了　　　　　　淨嚴<note place="inline">四十九載</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p></div1>
